EN: The atmosphere of this holiday is lower than what we expected.

ZH: 这个声音的音量小于噪音。
EN: The volume of this sound is lower than the noise.

ZH: 这个问题的难度小于我原先想象的。
EN: The difficulty of this problem is less than what I originally imagined.
